erson (without making a sound)</q></tr></example><example><quote>aw, k˳yd æʒæm mard fæwydaid?</quote><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>как она могла умереть так мгновенно?</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>how could she die so instantly?</q></tr><bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_MD"/><biblScope>1934 II 4</biblScope></bibl></example></exampleGrp><etym xml:lang="ru">Вероятно, из %iæ-cæm%i, где <ref type="xr" target="#entry_æ-"/> — негативная частица, а %i*cæm%i — какое-то забытое слово со значением ‘движение’, ‘жизнь’ и т. п.; ср. <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><lang/> <w>čam</w> <gloss><q>движение, покачивание при ходьбе</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="fa"><w/><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru">а также</note><note type="comment" xml:lang="en">also</note> <gloss><q>душа</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><w/> <gloss><q>энергия</q></gloss></mentioned>, .</etym><etym xml:lang="en">Probably, from %iæ-cæm%i, where <ref type="xr" target="#entry_æ-"/> is a negative particle and %i*cæm%i is some forgotten word with the meaning ‘movement’, ‘life’, etc .; cf. <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><lang/> <w>čam</w> <gloss><q>movement, swaying when walking</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="fa"><w/><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru">а также</note><note type="comment" xml:lang="en">also</note> <gloss><q>soul</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><w/> <gloss><q>energy</q></gloss></mentioned>, .</etym></entry></body></text></TEI>